Wednesday, October 24, 2001

MERIT DOCKET

01-1539. State ex rel. Untied v. Hoffman.

In Mandamus. On motion to consolidate case with 01-1501, State ex rel. Untied v. Hoffman, and on motion to dismiss. Motion to consolidate denied and motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
